14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bir bar&#351;ynda&nbsp;<b>kliniki
muayene,&nbsp;</b>lukman, duran skrotal damarlary gi&#328;eltmegi&#328; we we
zorlamadan pozisyonlar &yacute;alan derejesini baha ber&yacute;&auml;r
&yacute;umurtgalary &ouml;l&ccedil;egini skrotal ysy tespit.&nbsp;</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Warikosele bilen, testirler adat&ccedil;a
ki&ccedil;el&yacute;&auml;r, &yacute;&ouml;ne testird&auml;ki damarlar
&ouml;zleri daralsa, ulal&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Lukman kremasteriki refleksi&#328;,
&yacute;agny budu&#328; i&ccedil; &yacute;&uuml;z&uuml;nde saklanmagyna jogap
h&ouml;km&uuml;nde m&auml;zi&#328; &yacute;okary galdyrylmagyny
barlamaly.&nbsp;Varikoseli&#328; tapgyry n&auml;&ccedil;e &ouml;sen bolsa, bu
refleks &#351;on&ccedil;a az a&yacute;dyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a
g&ouml;zlegleri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>A
idrar&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>seb&auml;pli inflamatuar amaly idrar
protein barlygyny biler.&nbsp;Si&yacute;dikd&auml;ki gyzyl gan
&ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;klerini&#328; sanyny&#328; k&ouml;pelmegi
m&uuml;mkindir.&nbsp;<b>Meni&ntilde; der&#328;ewi&nbsp;</b>sany azalma we sperm
motilitesi belgilenen bolar.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Funksi&yacute;a,
radiasi&yacute;a we instrumental diagnostika</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>D&uuml;w&uuml;rtigi&#328;
ultrases barlagy m&auml;zi&#328;&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>ululygyny
kesgitlem&auml;ge, damarlardaky gan a&yacute;lany&#351;yny barlamaga we
patologiki ta&yacute;dan &uuml;&yacute;tgedilen damarlary&#328;
lokalizasi&yacute;asyny we a&yacute;ratynlygyny kesgitlem&auml;ge k&ouml;mek
eder.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Rahatsyzlygy we agyryny azaltmak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>D&uuml;w&uuml;rtige we m&auml;zi&#328; kadaly gan
&uuml;pj&uuml;n&ccedil;iligini dikeltmek;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&ouml;nelgesizligi bejermek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351; &yacute;oly we
gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Spirtli i&ccedil;giler
&ccedil;ilim &ccedil;ekmek we i&ccedil;mek, gan damarlaryna &yacute;aramaz
t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;r, gan damarlaryny hem &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine
al&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>I&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
i&#351;ine g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik edi&#328;, i&ccedil; gatamagyndan ga&ccedil;a
duru&#328;.&nbsp;Munu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in berhizde g&ouml;k
&ouml;n&uuml;mler, miweler we otlar g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde has k&ouml;p
s&uuml;&yacute;&uuml;m go&#351;mak, orta&ccedil;a fiziki i&#351;je&#328;lik
bilen me&#351;gullanmak maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Derman bejergisi,
esasan, spermatogenezi&#328; d&ouml;remegine itergi bermek &uuml;&ccedil;in operasi&yacute;adan
so&#328; ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Agyry azaltmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in lukman a&#351;akdakylary bell&auml;p biler:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>steroid d&auml;l &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y dermanlar;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>parasetamol.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Varikoseli&#328;
emboli&yacute;asy&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.&nbsp;Localerli anestezi astynda
&yacute;erine &yacute;etiril&yacute;&auml;r we uzak wagtlap hassahana
&yacute;erle&#351;dirilmegini talap etme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Thinum&#351;ak kateter, budu&#328; derisine we m&auml;zi&#328;
damaryna ki&ccedil;ijik kesik arkaly salyn&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Wena damarlaryny
sklerozla&yacute;an we gan a&yacute;lany&#351;yny b&ouml;kde&yacute;&auml;n
kateter arkaly sanjym edil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;N&auml;sag damar i&ccedil;inden
&yacute;apyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki
amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmanlar
varikoseli&#328; ikinji basgan&ccedil;agyndan ba&#351;lap hirurgiki bejergini
maslahat ber&yacute;&auml;rler.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le-de bolsa, n&auml;saga
&ouml;nelgesizlik diagnozy go&yacute;ulsa, operasi&yacute;a birinji etapda
g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Testikul&yacute;ar damarlary&#328; endoskopiki
baglany&#351;ygy&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.&nbsp;Endoskop,
lukmanlary&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen patologiki ta&yacute;dan
&uuml;&yacute;tgedilen damarlary baglany&#351;dyr&yacute;an ownuk b&ouml;lekler
arkaly girizil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Operasi&yacute;a &yacute;erli
anestezi&yacute;a astynda ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r we uzak wagtlap
hassahana &yacute;erle&#351;dirilmegini talap etme&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Wena damarlaryny a&yacute;yrmak bo&yacute;un&ccedil;a klassiki
amallar&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.&nbsp;Hirurgiki
&ccedil;emele&#351;m&auml; baglylykda birn&auml;&ccedil;e g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;
bar.&nbsp;Operasi&yacute;alar umumy n&auml;gilelik astynda
ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r we uzak wagtlap hassahana
&yacute;erle&#351;dirilmegini talap ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>H&auml;zirki
wagtda olar se&yacute;rek ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki bejergiden so&#328;,
spermatiki simi&#328; uzalmazlygy &uuml;&ccedil;in berk i&ccedil;ki e&#351;ik
ge&yacute;mek maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Ilkinji hepdelerde fiziki
i&#351;je&#328;ligi &ccedil;&auml;klendirmeli, &yacute;&ouml;ne fiziki
i&#351;je&#328;ligi saklamaly.&nbsp;Uzak wagtlap oturmak &yacute;a-da
&yacute;atmak damarlarda gan akmagyna zy&yacute;an &yacute;etirer.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Warikosele bejergisi
&ouml;nelgesizlik bilen baglany&#351;ykly ge&ccedil;irilen bolsa, bejergiden
so&#328; &uuml;&ccedil; a&yacute;dan gij&auml; galman g&ouml;wrelilik
ba&#351;lap bolar.&nbsp;Adaty spermatogenezi&#328; dikeldilmegi
&uuml;&ccedil;in n&auml;&ccedil;e wagt gerek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ouml;nelgesizlik&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>varikoseli&#328; i&#328;
k&ouml;p &yacute;a&yacute;ran &ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylygydyr.&nbsp;Wenoz gan
a&yacute;lany&#351;yny&#328; bozulmagy, spermy&#328; d&ouml;remegine
&yacute;aramaz t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;n skrotumy&#328; temperaturasyny
&yacute;okarlandyr&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Varikoseli&#328; birinji
basgan&ccedil;agynda &ouml;nelgesizlik &ouml;s&uuml;p biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- warikosele
bilen testosteron &ouml;n&uuml;m&ccedil;iligi azal&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Testiki atrofi&yacute;a&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>varikoseli&#328;
&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;nji basgan&ccedil;agyny&#328; &ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly
h&auml;si&yacute;etidir.&nbsp;&Ccedil;agalykda &yacute;a-da
&yacute;etginjeklikde atrofi&yacute;a &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;an
bolsa, &yacute;etginjeklik prosesi bozul&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gematoma&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, patologiki ta&yacute;dan
&uuml;&yacute;tg&auml;n damarlary&#328; &ouml;z-&ouml;z&uuml;nden &yacute;a-da
trawmatiki &yacute;arylmagy we skrotumda gan &yacute;ygnanmagy netijesinde
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;an se&yacute;rek bir
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylykdyr.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni
aly&#351; &ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Urolog tarapyndan
profilaktiki barlag her &yacute;yl 15-25 &yacute;a&#351; aralygyndaky erkekler
we 50 &yacute;a&#351;dan so&#328; ge&ccedil;irilmelidir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>I&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak &uuml;&ccedil;in erbet endikleri, fiziki
i&#351;je&#328;ligi, dogry i&yacute;mitlenmegi we i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni
kadala&#351;dyrmak m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aklama</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Kesgitlemek
amatly.&nbsp;Wagtynda hirurgiki bejergisi n&auml;saglary&#328; 90-99%
-ini&#328; doly bejerilmegine getir&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmandan ha&yacute;sy
soraglary bermeli?</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Operasi&yacute;adan so&#328; varikoseli&#328;
